---
// EmbeddingModels.astro — Comparison of embedding models with expandable details
---

<div class="em-wrap">
  <h3 class="em-title">Picking the Right Embedding Model</h3>
  <p class="em-sub">Not all embeddings are equal. Click each to see the trade-offs.</p>

  <div class="em-stack">
    <details class="em-card em-card--green">
      <summary class="em-header">
        <div class="em-badge">Fast</div>
        <div class="em-info">
          <span class="em-name">text-embedding-3-small</span>
          <span class="em-dims">1,536 dims · $0.02 / 1M tokens</span>
        </div>
        <div class="em-score">
          <span class="em-score-label">Quality</span>
          <div class="em-score-bar"><div class="em-score-fill" style="--w:72%;--c:#4ade80"></div></div>
        </div>
        <span class="em-arrow">▼</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="em-body">
        <p>Best for: prototyping, internal tools, high-volume search. Good enough for 80% of use cases. Lowest cost, fastest inference.</p>
        <div class="em-stats">
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Latency:</strong> ~15ms</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>MTEB Score:</strong> 62.3</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Max tokens:</strong> 8,191</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="em-card em-card--cyan">
      <summary class="em-header">
        <div class="em-badge em-badge--cyan">Balanced</div>
        <div class="em-info">
          <span class="em-name">text-embedding-3-large</span>
          <span class="em-dims">3,072 dims · $0.13 / 1M tokens</span>
        </div>
        <div class="em-score">
          <span class="em-score-label">Quality</span>
          <div class="em-score-bar"><div class="em-score-fill" style="--w:88%;--c:#06b6d4"></div></div>
        </div>
        <span class="em-arrow">▼</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="em-body">
        <p>Best for: production RAG, customer-facing search, multilingual content. Significant quality jump over small. Worth 6x cost for precision-critical apps.</p>
        <div class="em-stats">
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Latency:</strong> ~25ms</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>MTEB Score:</strong> 64.6</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Max tokens:</strong> 8,191</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="em-card em-card--purple">
      <summary class="em-header">
        <div class="em-badge em-badge--purple">Open</div>
        <div class="em-info">
          <span class="em-name">all-MiniLM-L6-v2</span>
          <span class="em-dims">384 dims · Free (self-hosted)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="em-score">
          <span class="em-score-label">Quality</span>
          <div class="em-score-bar"><div class="em-score-fill" style="--w:58%;--c:#818cf8"></div></div>
        </div>
        <span class="em-arrow">▼</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="em-body">
        <p>Best for: air-gapped environments, budget-zero projects, edge deployments. Run on your own GPU. Lower quality but zero API costs and full data privacy.</p>
        <div class="em-stats">
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Latency:</strong> ~5ms (local GPU)</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>MTEB Score:</strong> 56.3</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Max tokens:</strong> 256</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="em-card em-card--amber">
      <summary class="em-header">
        <div class="em-badge em-badge--amber">Best</div>
        <div class="em-info">
          <span class="em-name">Cohere embed-v3</span>
          <span class="em-dims">1,024 dims · $0.10 / 1M tokens</span>
        </div>
        <div class="em-score">
          <span class="em-score-label">Quality</span>
          <div class="em-score-bar"><div class="em-score-fill" style="--w:93%;--c:#f59e0b"></div></div>
        </div>
        <span class="em-arrow">▼</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="em-body">
        <p>Best for: highest quality search, multilingual, classification tasks. Currently top of MTEB leaderboard. Supports search and classification modes for optimized embeddings.</p>
        <div class="em-stats">
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Latency:</strong> ~20ms</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>MTEB Score:</strong> 66.3</span>
          <span class="em-stat"><strong>Max tokens:</strong> 512</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .em-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .em-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .em-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }
  .em-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }

  .em-card { border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #334155; overflow: hidden; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
  .em-card[open] { border-color: #475569; }
  .em-card--green[open] { border-color: #4ade8030; }
  .em-card--cyan[open] { border-color: #06b6d430; }
  .em-card--purple[open] { border-color: #818cf830; }
  .em-card--amber[open] { border-color: #f59e0b30; }

  .em-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 16px;
    cursor: pointer; list-style: none; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .em-header::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .em-header::marker { content: ''; }

  .em-badge {
    font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: monospace; padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #4ade80; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12);
  }
  .em-badge--cyan { color: #06b6d4; background: rgba(6,182,212,0.12); }
  .em-badge--purple { color: #818cf8; background: rgba(129,140,248,0.12); }
  .em-badge--amber { color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); }

  .em-info { flex: 1; }
  .em-name { display: block; color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; font-family: monospace; }
  .em-dims { display: block; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.6rem; font-family: monospace; margin-top: 2px; }

  .em-score { width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .em-score-label { display: block; color: #475569; font-size: 0.45rem; font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .em-score-bar { height: 4px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
  .em-score-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; width: 0; animation: emGrow 1s ease-out 0.3s forwards; background: var(--c); }

  .em-arrow { color: #475569; font-size: 0.7rem; transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .em-card[open] .em-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  .em-body { padding: 14px 16px; }
  .em-body p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; }

  .em-stats { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
  .em-stat { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.65rem; font-family: monospace; }
  .em-stat strong { color: #94a3b8; }

  @keyframes emGrow { to { width: var(--w); } }
</style>
